column1:
You can decide how do you want to calculate the shipping cost when an order merge several bought products by a customer.
"Highest Price": it will find which product has the highest cost for the shipping and will take only this one for the calculation.
"Cumulative": it will calculate the shipping cost based on the configuration you did in the products listing for each article and will combine them.
column2:
You can decide how do you want to calculate the shipping cost when an order merge several bought products by a customer.
"Highest Price": it will find which product has the highest cost for the shipping and will take only this one for the calculation.
"Cumulative": it will calculate the shipping cost based on the configuration you did in the products listing for each article and will combine them.
